snippet.title: FORGET CATS! Funny PUGS are here to MAKE YOU LAUGH! - Funny DOG compilation
snippet.description:
Pugs are so funny, they never fail to make us laugh! This funny pug compilation is simply the hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these pugs play, behave, fail, sleep,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
